      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was just looking at some stuff about the heat death of the universe and it honestly just makes everything feel so stupid. like why do we even bother trying to build anything or feel anything when in the end the entire universe is just gonna be cold and empty and nothing we ever did will have left a single trace. it feels like we're just running on a treadmill for no reason.",
